
cclive
============

cclive is a command line tool for downloading videos from Youtube and other
similar video websites that require Adobe Flash to view the content. It has
low memory footprint compared to other similar tools and small CPU load. Its
advanced feature-set makes cclive the perfect command line video download
tool.

cclive is a rewrite of the clive software in C++, it is free software licensed
under the GPLv3. cclive is cross-platform, it runs on Linux and Unix-like
operating systems, as well as on MSWindows.

WWW: <http://cclive.googlecode.com/>
GIT: <git://repo.or.cz/cclive.git>
